{"prompt": "Produce a platform for a digital art marketplace. The design should be innovative, with an electric yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Digital Art Marketplace</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #ffff00; /* Electric Yellow */\n            --secondary-color: #f0f000; /* A lighter, less saturated yellow */\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark background */\n            --text-color: #ffffff; /* White text */\n            --accent-color: #333333; /* Dark accent for elements */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: repeating-linear-gradient(\n                45deg,\n                rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.2),\n                rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.2) 10px,\n                rgba(240, 240, 0, 0.2) 10px,\n                rgba(240, 240, 0, 0.2) 20px\n            );\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            color: #ccc;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        .artworks-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .artwork-card {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .artwork-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .artwork-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .artwork-info {\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .artwork-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .artwork-info p {\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            color: #bbb;\n        }\n\n        .artwork-info .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: #aaa;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            box-shadow: 0 -2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                font-size: 1rem;\n                margin: 0 0.5rem;\n            }\n            .hero-section h2 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n            .hero-section p {\n                font-size: 1rem;\n            }\n            .artworks-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n            nav {\n                display: flex;\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            }\n            .hero-section h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8rem;\n            }\n            .cta-button {\n                padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;\n                font-size: 1rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Ethereal Canvas</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#featured\">Featured</a>\n            <a href=\"#browse\">Browse</a>\n            <a href=\"#sell\">Sell</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"container hero-section\">\n        <h2>Discover & Collect Unique Digital Art</h2>\n        <p>Your portal to a world of breathtaking digital creations. Explore, purchase, and own a piece of the future.</p>\n        <a href=\"#browse\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Artworks</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\">\n        <h2 id=\"featured\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2.2rem; color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 2rem;\">Featured Collections</h2>\n        <div class=\"artworks-grid\">\n            <div class=\"artwork-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/ffff00/1a1a1a?text=Abstract+Flow\" alt=\"Abstract Artwork\">\n                <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                    <h3>Abstract Flow</h3>\n                    <p>By PixelDreamer</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$150.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"artwork-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/f0f000/1a1a1a?text=Cyberpunk+City\" alt=\"Cyberpunk Artwork\">\n                <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                    <h3>Cyberpunk City</h3>\n                    <p>By NeonArtist</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$220.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"artwork-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/ffff00/1a1a1a?text=Galactic+Voyage\" alt=\"Sci-Fi Artwork\">\n                <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                    <h3>Galactic Voyage</h3>\n                    <p>By AstroArt</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$180.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"artwork-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/f0f000/1a1a1a?text=Nature's+Whisper\" alt=\"Nature Artwork\">\n                <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                    <h3>Nature's Whisper</h3>\n                    <p>By EarthSculptor</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$130.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\" id=\"browse\" style=\"margin-top: 4rem;\">\n        <h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2.2rem; color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 2rem;\">Browse All Artworks</h2>\n        <div class=\"artworks-grid\">\n            <div class=\"artwork-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/ffff00/1a1a1a?text=Digital+Portrait\" alt=\"Digital Portrait\">\n                <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                    <h3>Digital Portrait</h3>\n                    <p>By PortraitMaster</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$100.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"artwork-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/f0f000/1a1a1a?text=Surreal+Dream\" alt=\"Surreal Artwork\">\n                <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                    <h3>Surreal Dream</h3>\n                    <p>By DreamWeaver</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$200.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"artwork-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/ffff00/1a1a1a?text=Geometric+Wonder\" alt=\"Geometric Artwork\">\n                <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                    <h3>Geometric Wonder</h3>\n                    <p>By ShapeShifter</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$160.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"artwork-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/f0f000/1a1a1a?text=Fantasy+Realm\" alt=\"Fantasy Artwork\">\n                <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                    <h3>Fantasy Realm</h3>\n                    <p>By MythicPainter</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$190.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\" id=\"sell\" style=\"margin-top: 4rem; background-color: var(--accent-color); padding: 3rem; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.2rem; color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\">Ready to Showcase Your Talent?</h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; color: #ccc; margin-bottom: 2rem;\">Join our community of creators and reach a global audience. Sell your digital art with ease.</p>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Start Selling</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"about\">\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Ethereal Canvas. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>A platform for innovative digital art. | Contact us: <a href=\"mailto:info@etherealcanvas.com\">info@etherealcanvas.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic JS for potential future enhancements, e.g., smooth scrolling\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}